https://guidetoiceland.is/book-holiday-trips/jokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast</a><br />\n如果兩日一夜既話我會推薦呢個<br />\n雖然話golden circle係必去,但我去嗰時真係太多人<br />\n想靜靜地睇下景影下相都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔去golden circle，仲有咩景點推薦？因為預左5日，冇理由市内玩3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋冰島冬天會唔會好凍？你去果陣點著？"},{"pid":"0013eca95d3f89ee9f39d19cac8d863a06dc5e54","tid":284963,"uid":51744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://guidetoiceland.is/book-holiday-trips/jokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fguidetoiceland.is%2Fbook-holiday-trips%2Fjokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast&d=6wfPHStBatE9TzfwlFmcfROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f710006d\" target=\"_blank\">https://guidetoiceland.is/book-holiday-trips/jokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast</a><br />\n如果兩日一夜既話我會推薦呢個<br />\n雖然話golden circle係必去,但我去嗰時真係太多人<br />\n想靜靜地睇下景影下相都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔去golden circle，仲有咩景點推薦？因為預左5日，冇理由市内玩3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋冰島冬天會唔會好凍？你去果陣點著？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一月去天昏地暗。我試過聖誕去，十一點開始天光，四點天黑齊。你唔去GOLDEN CIRCLE都無乜嘢好行，你可以去BLUE LAGOON浸兩三粒鐘。基本上冬天去好迆。<br />\n唔算太凍，－5至5度，不過好大風，好似香港掛三號波咁。"},{"pid":"47cf3a9c746169f20352d7e658126449868a360e","tid":284963,"uid":15512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:56:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://guidetoiceland.is/book-holiday-trips/jokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fguidetoiceland.is%2Fbook-holiday-trips%2Fjokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast&d=6wfPHStBatE9TzfwlFmcfROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f710006d\" target=\"_blank\">https://guidetoiceland.is/book-holiday-trips/jokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast</a><br />\n如果兩日一夜既話我會推薦呢個<br />\n雖然話golden circle係必去,但我去嗰時真係太多人<br />\n想靜靜地睇下景影下相都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔去golden circle，仲有咩景點推薦？因為預左5日，冇理由市内玩3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋冰島冬天會唔會好凍？你去果陣點著？</blockquote><br />\n市內一日就玩得哂<br />\nGuide to iceland可以搵自己想玩嗰啲(e.g.騎馬浮潛)<br />\n極光團就建議盡早報,第一日睇唔到都可以有第二次機會<br />\n我上次去時係3月,不過我諗同1月差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n衣著方面我就heattech打底,入面一件抓毛/衛衣<br />\n再加件防風防水既褸<br />\n褲就保暖打底+防水褲,最好就有埋頸巾手套啦<br />\n怕凍就帶暖包去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cceb68bb45ee31c4f7600524b5612523e24aebce","tid":284963,"uid":15512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://guidetoiceland.is/book-holiday-trips/jokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fguidetoiceland.is%2Fbook-holiday-trips%2Fjokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast&d=6wfPHStBatE9TzfwlFmcfROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f710006d\" target=\"_blank\">https://guidetoiceland.is/book-holiday-trips/jokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast</a><br />\n如果兩日一夜既話我會推薦呢個<br />\n雖然話golden circle係必去,但我去嗰時真係太多人<br />\n想靜靜地睇下景影下相都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔去golden circle，仲有咩景點推薦？因為預左5日，冇理由市内玩3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋冰島冬天會唔會好凍？你去果陣點著？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一月去天昏地暗。我試過聖誕去，十一點開始天光，四點天黑齊。你唔去GOLDEN CIRCLE都無乜嘢好行，你可以去BLUE LAGOON浸兩三粒鐘。基本上冬天去好迆。<br />\n唔算太凍，－5至5度，不過好大風，好似香港掛三號波咁。</blockquote><br />\nBlue lagoon都值得一去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0f11bc5dfc00eeb2841337475eaa823ad4875f","tid":284963,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://guidetoiceland.is/book-holiday-trips/jokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fguidetoiceland.is%2Fbook-holiday-trips%2Fjokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast&d=6wfPHStBatE9TzfwlFmcfROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f710006d\" target=\"_blank\">https://guidetoiceland.is/book-holiday-trips/jokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast</a><br />\n如果兩日一夜既話我會推薦呢個<br />\n雖然話golden circle係必去,但我去嗰時真係太多人<br />\n想靜靜地睇下景影下相都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔去golden