kulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast&d=6wfPHStBatE9TzfwlFmcfROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f710006d\" target=\"_blank\">https://guidetoiceland.is/book-holiday-trips/jokulsarlon-and-ice-caving-two-day-package-tour-along-the-south-coast</a><br />\n如果兩日一夜既話我會推薦呢個<br />\n雖然話golden circle係必去,但我去嗰時真係太多人<br />\n想靜靜地睇下景影下相都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔去golden circle，仲有咩景點推薦？因為預左5日，冇理由市内玩3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋冰島冬天會唔會好凍？你去果陣點著？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一月去天昏地暗。我試過聖誕去，十一點開始天光，四點天黑齊。你唔去GOLDEN CIRCLE都無乜嘢好行，你可以去BLUE LAGOON浸兩三粒鐘。基本上冬天去好迆。<br />\n唔算太凍，－5至5度，不過好大風，好似香港掛三號波咁。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打去冰島洗左幾多錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去五日，唔計機票，大概四五千啦"},{"pid":"68b4bf65333f31fef3484163b724fbf21fdf56dd","tid":284963,"uid":122988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T22:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Extreme Iceland 個d tour都幾好，小形d，住得好過guide to Iceland 。<br />\n不過冬天好易撞到大冬雪會阻到行程。我上次去就tour臨尾果日要cancel 行程即時返雷克雅未克，結果golden circle 都冇得去。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問cancel左係咪冇得退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多數有 報個時要睇 極光tour睇唔到會話你好似1年(?)之內可以再join過 <br />\n<br />\n2月去個時倫敦落雪冰島無落雪 佢地話冬天推遲左本身啲景點可以再靚啲<br />\njoin過extreme 2日1夜去南部行冰山睇黑沙灘瀑布 幾好 佢回程話如果極光指數高會又想睇極光可以再同你追 不過個日唔好天<br />\n我係bluelagoon+市區1日黃金圈1日南部2日 食左2個杯面 市區有subway食 <br />\n黃金圈南部個d就無計見到餐廳都要食架啦"},{"pid":"da2c76ca4d468d893aeaef645e671201206171b2","tid":284963,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"食野好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3eb31df86f5d8f90d87bbb5f1d3a17fee30dcd9","tid":284963,"uid":52993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"其實tour最好係去報hostel入面個d<br />\n少人好多多好多interaction<br />\nKex hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f12a3c0860597f93144a5c621d31901627b2042","tid":284963,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>極光團唔洗考慮 係冰島睇到極光既機會太低<br />\n咁短時間搵人自駕都唔洗考慮 報2days tour已經好過搵個唔熟環境既人自駕七日<br />\n如果你五日建議你可以第一日到 用兩三個鐘行市內 再報3-4日tours 貴但值 <br />\n<br />\n三月去完預太少時間凈係join到2days tour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n市內睇唔睇到極光？"},{"pid":"7e2e28389272e4e361f42f09f56130b5de520f21","tid":284963,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Extreme Iceland 個d tour都幾好，小形d，住得好過guide to Iceland 。<br />\n不過冬天好易撞到大冬雪會阻到行程。我上次去就tour臨尾果日要cancel 行程即時返雷克雅未克，結果golden circle 都冇得去。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問cancel左係咪冇得退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多數有 報個時要睇 極光tour睇唔到會話你好似1年(?)之內可以再join過 <br />\n<br />\n2月去個時倫敦落雪冰島無落雪 佢地話冬天推遲左本身啲景點可以再靚啲<br />\njoin過extreme 2日1夜去南部行冰山睇黑沙灘瀑布 幾好 佢回程話如果極光指數高會又想睇極光可以再同你追 不過個日唔好天<br />\n我係